function claim() {
  const data = table.data;
  let highestLeagueAppsPlayer = null;

  data.forEach((playerInfo, index) => {

    if(playerInfo[1] == 'df'){
      playerLeagueApps = parseInt(playerInfo[2])
    }
    else{
      playerLeagueApps = parseInt(playerInfo[3])
    }

    const currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer = highestLeagueAppsPlayer;
    if(currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer === null || playerLeagueApps > currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer) {

      highestLeagueAppsPlayer = playerLeagueApps
      relevantCells.push({row_index: index, column_name:"league apps"});
    }
  });

  data.forEach((playerInfo, index) => {

    if(playerInfo[1] == 'df'){
      playerLeagueApps = parseInt(playerInfo[2])
    }
    else{
      playerLeagueApps = parseInt(playerInfo[3])
    }

    const currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer = highestLeagueAppsPlayer;
    if(currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer === playerLeagueApps && playerInfo[0] != "chris topping") {

      relevantCells.push({row_index: index, column_name:"league apps"});
    }
  });

  data.forEach((playerInfo, index) => {
    const currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer = highestLeagueAppsPlayer;
    if(playerInfo[1] == 'df'){
      playerLeagueGoals = parseInt(playerInfo[2])
    }
    else{
      playerLeagueGoals = parseInt(playerInfo[5])
    }

    if(currentHighestLeagueAppsPlayer === playerLeagueGoals && playerInfo[0] != "dave sutton") {

      relevantCells.push({row_index: index, column_name:"league goals"});
    }
  });

  return JSON.stringify({
    answer: highestLeagueAppsPlayer == null || highestLeagueAppsPlayer == data[0][2]? "FALSE": "TRUE",
    relevant_cells:relevantCells

  })
}
